20a.m.%20PT%20for%20a%201%3A1%20meeting%20with%20their%20manager%20later%20that%20same%20morning.%20We%20know%20the%20timing%20here%20is%20difficult%20%E2%80%93%20waiting%20between%20now%20and%20tomorrow%20to%20understand%20whether%20you're%20impacted%20is%20far%20from%20ideal%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20a%20considerate%20notification%20process%20that%20accommodates%20all%20time%20zones.%20We%20will%20be%20doing%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20support%20our%20impacted%20colleagues%20through%20the%20separation%20process%2C%20including%20severance%2C%20eligibility%20for%20Rivian-paid%20COBRA%20benefits%20coverage%20and%20access%20to%20job%20placement%20services.%20Also%2C%20anyone%20impacted%20tomorrow%20will%20still%20be%20eligible%20for%20our%20FY'23%20bonus.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20recognize%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20isn't%20easy.%20I'm%20thankful%20for%20everyone's%20contributions%2C%20and%20for%20those%20who%20leave%20us%2C%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20you%20deeply%20for%20everything%20you've%20done%20for%20Rivian%2C%20and%20for%20what%20you've%20done%20to%20advance%20our%20mission.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERJ%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-cutting-10-of-workforce-faces-slower-growth-than-predicted-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708556469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6565c048fe5bc6545ebcd35e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-cutting-10-of-workforce-faces-slower-growth-than-predicted-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electric%20vehicle%20maker%20Rivian%20announced%20its%202023%20fourth%20quarter%20earnings%20Wednesday%2C%20revealing%20a%20profit%20loss%20and%20less%20growth%20than%20analysts%20forecasted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20E