rring%20Catherine%20Zeta-Jones%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rakontur.com%2Fconfessions-of-a-cocaine-cowboy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estage%20play%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Michael%20Corleone%20Blanco%2C%20the%20famed%20drug%20kingpin's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-sons-now-michael-blanco-lawsuit-netflix-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20surviving%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20learned%20quickly%20that%20true-crime%20fame%20is%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20Corben%20was%20making%20his%20first%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20the%20franchise%20now%20includes%20two%20more%20documentaries%20and%20a%20Netflix%20series%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBlanco%20was%20also%20pitching%20his%20family's%20story%20around%20Hollywood.%20But%20Corben's%20documentary%20found%20audiences%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20my%20archnemesis%20because%20they%20were%20doing%20what%20I%20was%20planning%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanco%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20Corben%2C%20his%20producing%20partner%20Alfred%20Spellman%2C%20and%20editor%20David%20Cypkin%2C%20who%20make%20up%20the%20Miami-based%20media%20studio%20Rakontur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20almost%20twenty%20years%2C%20and%20Corben%20and%20Blanco%20have%20joined%20forces%20for%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Real%20Griselda%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20which%20picks%20apart%20the%20Netflix%20hit%20series%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-son-michael-corleone-blanco-netflix-series-inaccurate-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGriselda%26quot%3B%20to%20reveal%20what's%20fact%20and%20what's%20fiction%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20eight%20episodes%20of%20the%20podcast%2C%20which%20is%20hosted%20by%20Corben%2C%20Blanco%20points%20out%20the%20creative%20liberties%20taken%20in%20%26quot%3BGriselda%2C%26quot%3B%20often%20backing%20them%20up%20with%20colorful%20stories.%20He%20says%20his%20mother%20never%20lit%20kilos%20of%20cocaine%20on%20fire%20in%20an%20empty%20pool%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20notes%20that%20some%20of%20the%20murders%20were%20more%20gruesome%20in%20real%20life%20than%20in%20the%20show.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-husbands-killed-dario-sepulveda-alberto-bravo-carlos-trujillo-netflix-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather's%20murder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20real%20life%2C%20young%20Michael%20didn't%20just%20see%20it%20happen%3B%20his%20father%20held%20him%20tight%20in%20his%20arms%2C%20shielding%20him%20from%20the%20gunshots%20that%20killed%20him%20(the%20hit%20on%20his%20father%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20ordered%20by%20Griselda).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast%20also%20sheds%20some%20light%20on%20Michael's%20life%20following%20the%20events%20shown%20in%20the%20Netflix%20series.%20He%20lived%20with%20foster%20families%20while%20his%20mother%20served%20three%2020-year%20prison%20sentences%20for%20murder%20concurrently%20(upon%20her%20release%20in%202004%2C%20she%20was%20deported%20to%20Colombia%2C%20where%20she%20died%20of%20a%20gunshot%20wound%20in%202012).%20He%20briefly%20followed%20in%20his%20family's%20footsteps%20and%20dabbled%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Blanco%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20it%20by%20going%20legit%3A%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymotherthegodmother.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20a%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20he's%20developing%20TV%20shows%20and%20movies.%20He's%20eager%20to%20prove%20that%20there%20is%20a%20future%20for%20the%20Blanco%20name%20beyond%20its%20notorious%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20from%20a%20drug%20trafficking%20family%2C%20and%20you're%20fucking%20Miami%20monarchy%2C%20Miami%20royalty%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20for%20you%20to%20understand%20that%20that%20life%20has%20gone%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanco%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20evolve%20as%20a%20man.%20And%20the%20only%20way%20I%20could%20evolve%20was%20legalizing%20my%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20over%20the%20phone%20with%20Corben%20and%20Blanco%20about%20why%20they%20teamed%20up%20for%20a%20podcast%2C%20the%20actor%20Blanco%20believes%20did%20the%20best%20portrayal%20of%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20how%20Corben%20got%20close%20to%20becoming%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20cocaine%20godmother's%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20podcast%20makes%20it%20sound%20like%20you%20two%20have%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years.%20Billy%2C%20when%20was%20your%20first%20interaction%20with%20Michael%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20goes%20way%20back.%20It%20was%20probably%20between%20the%20release%20of%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%202.%26quot%3B%20Michael%2C%20does%20that%20sound%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah.%20I%20would%20say%202006%20or%202007.%20I%20remember%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20walking%20to%20The%20Colony%20Theatre%20for%20the%20second%20movie.%20Still%20being%20part%20of%20that%20underground%20world%20back%20then%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20statement.%20So%2C%20I%20showed%20up%20with%2020-30%20goons.%20I%20let%20people%20know%20South%20Beach%20was%20my%20stomping%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichael%2C%20you%20speak%20on%20the%20podcast%20about%20the%20animosity%20you%20had%20toward%20Billy%20and%20his%20filmmaking%20partners%20at%20that%20time.%20When%20did%20you%20figure%20out%20that%20you%20could%20also%20make%20money%20off%20your%20family%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20that%20long%20after%20that.%20One%20thing%20my%20mother%20taught%20me%20was%20how%20to%20pivot.%20From%20the%20moment%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20one%20of%20their%20movie's%20investors%20for%20the%20first%20movie%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20had%20to%20put%20some%20pep%20in%20my%20step%20and%20get%20on%20their%20level.%20I%20was%20a%20rookie%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20will%20say%20the%20smartest%20thing%20I%20ever%20did%20was%20not%20to%20listen%20to%20my%20lawyer%20or%20my%20mother%20and%20put%20a%20cease%20and%20desist%20on%20the%20first%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20movie.%20I%20knew%20that%20one%20day%2C%20the%20Griselda%20Blanco%20story%20and%20the%20Blanco%20family%20story%20would%20have%20to%20be%20told%2C%20and%20with%20them%20already%20telling%20some%20of%20the%20story%2C%20it%20was%20going%20to%20help%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20when%20Billy%20put%20together%20the%20play%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcocaine-cowboys-being-made-into-a-play-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConfessions%20of%20a%20Cocaine%20Cowboy%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%202019%2C%20which%20also%20played%20at%20The%20Colony%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20Billy%2C%20Alfred%2C%20and%20Dave%20as%20my%20archnemesis%20anymore.%20I%20remember%20having%20a%20drink%20with%20Billy%20back%20then%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20thank%20you.%20Because%20if%20it%20wasn't%20for%20that%20wave%20you%20created%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20right%20now.%20Because%20now%20I%20make%20the%20big%20bucks.%20It's%20a%20full-circle%20moment%2C%20being%20on%20this%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20as%20much%20as%20Michael%20and%20his%20mother%20felt%20that%20something%20had%20been%20taken%20from%20them%2C%20remember%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocala.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2F2006%2F10%2F28%2Ffilm-on-drug-trade-a-bootleg-hit%2F31173480007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank