%2C%20dehydrated%20texture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20take%20your%20time%20while%20diffusing.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20us%20have%20busy%20schedules%2C%20so%20time%20isn't%20always%20on%20our%20side.%20In%20the%20event%20that%20you're%20in%20desperate%20need%20of%20a%20quick%20dry%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20the%20health%20of%20your%20curls%2C%20The%20DevaDiffuser%20by%20Deva%20Curl%20will%20do%20the%20trick.%20DevaCurl's%20hand-shaped%20diffuser%20is%20one%20of%20a%20kind%E2%80%94%20it's%20literally%20patented%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20structure%20is%20designed%20to%20target%20the%20roots%2C%20helping%20to%20dry%20curls%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20travel%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20constantly%20on%20the%20go%20but%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20curls%20fresh%20during%20travel%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20small%20tool%20with%20a%20diffuser%20that%20you%20can%20easily%20store%20in%20your%20suitcase.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-travel-hair-dryers%5C%22%3Etravel%20hair%20dryer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20fuss%20with%20buying%20a%20diffuser%20that%20fits%2C%20this%20is%20the%20perfect%20tool%20since%20it%20comes%20all%20in%20one.%20Revlon's%201875W%20Natural%20Texture%20Diffuser%20Hair%20Dryer%20is%20probably%20the%20cutest%20hair%20dryer%20you'll%20ever%20see%2C%20plus%20it's%20only%20%2435.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20traveling%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20you%20want%20to%20do%20is%20spend%20endless%20time%20in%20your%20hotel%20bathroom%20styling%20your%20hair%2C%20so%20this%20tool%20definitely%20comes%20in%20handy%20as%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20dry%20your%20hair%20quickly%20and%20effectively.%20Designed%20with%201875%20watts%2C%20Revlon's%20diffuser%20has%20a%20super%20strong%20airflow%2C%20and%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20dryer%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20most%2C%20allowing%20air%20to%20spread%20widely%20across%20the%20hair.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20feature%20of%20this%20diffuser%20is%20that%20it's%20crafted%20with%20tourmaline%20technology%2C%20which%20boosts%20the%20output%20of%20negative%20ions%2C%20taming%20frizz%20and%20helping%20curls%20to%20retain%20their%20moisture%2C%20shiny%2C%20and%20smooth%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20versatile%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20mesmerizing%20qualities%20of%20curly%20hair%20is%20its%20capacity%20for%20versatility%E2%80%94%20ringlets%20and%20spirals%20can%20shapeshift%20into%20various%20hairstyles%2C%20from%20twists%2C%20braids%2C%20blowouts%2C%20and%20more.%20With%20such%20an%20array%20of%20hairstyles%2C%20curly%20heads%20need%20a%20beauty%20tool%20that%20will%20match%20that%20energy.%20That's%20when%20Shark's%20Flexible%20Style%20Hair%20Blow%20Dryer%20%26amp%3B%20Multi-Styler%20comes%20into%20play.%20Unlike%20other%20dryers%2C%20this%20one%20comes%20with%20an%20array%20of%20diffusers%20that%20are%20great%20for%20curly%20hair.%20It%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20traditional%2C%20pronged%2C%20bowl-shaped%20diffuser%20that%20can%20create%20defined%20curls%E2%80%94%20whether%20you%20have%20tighter%20textures%20or%20looser%20strands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20oval%20brush%2C%20which%20can%20smooth%2C%20defrizz%2C%20and%20add%20volume%20to%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuto-wrap%20curlers%20create%20voluminous%20waves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20styling%20concentrator%20attachment%2C%20which%20can%20help%20to%20form%20a%20smooth%20blowout%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20volume%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20thing%20curly-haired%20folks%20aren't%20usually%20worried%20about%2C%20it's%20achieving%20volume.%20Whether%20you%20have%20tighter%20coils%20or%20looser%20waves%2C%20the%20spiral-like%20shape%20of%20curly%20strands%20automatically%20adds%20a%20sense%20of%20natural%20dimension.%20But%20there's%20no%20harm%20in%20enhancing%20what's%20already%20there!%20Thanks%20to%20Segbeauty's%20Hair%20Diffuser%2C%20creating%20a%20voluminous%20look%20is%20easier%20than%20ever.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Segbeauty%20Hair%20Diffuser%20is%20great%20for%20volume%20because%20it%20distributes%20heat%20evenly%20and%20has%20a%20larger%20bowl%20for%20hair%20to%20sit%20in%2C%20which%20also%20helps%20cut%20down%20on%20drying%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20hairstylist%20Cassandra%20Olivia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20dispersing%20steady%20airflow%2C%20large%20diffuser%20bowls%20are%20also%20great%20for%20drying%20and%20defining%20long%20hair.%20Those%20with%20lengthy%20curls%20know%20that%20diffusing%20can%20be%20a%20hassle%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20dealing%20with%20an%20attachment%20with%20a%20shallow%20bowl%20with%20short%20prongs.%20Diffusers%20designed%20in%20this%20way%20often%20cause%20hair%20strands%20to%20spill%20over%20the%20bowl's%20sides%2C%20leading%20to%20uneven%20drying%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20curl%20definition.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20someone%20with%20long%20hair%20who%20is%20looking%20to%20enhance%20the%20volume%20of%20your%20stands%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20add%20this%20product%20to%20your%20shopping%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20eliminating%20frizz%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20spiral-like%20shape%20of%20curls%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20natural%20oils%20to%20spread%20from%20your%20scalp%20throughout%20your%20hair%20strands%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20moisture%20and%20increased%20dryness.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20frizz%20is%20inevitable%2C%20but%20there%20are%20certainly%20ways%20to%20manage%20wispy%20strands.%20Hair%20stylist%20Cassandra%20Olivia%20notes%20that%20the%20first%20step%20is%20to%20apply%20a%20leave-in%20product%20before%20diffusing%20curls%20to%20help%20enhance%20their%20shape%20as%20they%20dry%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20apply%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-60849-20%26h%3Daddf9aea5dfe89c6fadfbe8c9222c020f3c8adf5f37325d0e8f96d947aef7b17%26postID%3D64bac45d0ccc0c435a05ccfd%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-diffusers-for-curly-hair%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526xs%253D1%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.leafandflower.com%25252Fproducts%25252Flf043-con%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELEAF%20%2B%20FLOWER%20CBD%20Instant%20Curl%20Defining%20Cream%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20my%20client's%20hair%20before%20diffusing%20as%20it%20helps%20to%20fortify%20curls%2C%20locking%20in%20their%20shape%20and%20creating%20a%20flexible%20hold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20you%20need%20to%20help%20to%20lock%20in%20moisture%20and%20define%20the%20curl's%20shape%20with%20a%20proper%20diffuser%20tool%2C%20such%20as%20Laifen's%20Swift%20High%20Speed%20Hair%20Dryer%20Diffuser%2C%20which%20we%20think%20is%20the%20best%20diffuser%20for%20eliminating%20frizz%20on%20curly%20hair.%20One%20of%20the%20great%20hallmarks%20of%20Laifen's%20Diffuser%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20enhance%20shine%20and%20tackle%20frizz.%20From%20first-hand%20experience%2C%20I%20can%20attest%20to%20the%20magic%20of%20Laifen%E2%80%94%20I%20use%20this%20diffuser%20after%20I%20wash%20and%20condition%20my%20hair%2C%20and%20the%20final%20look%20always%20blows%20me%20away.%20After%20drying%2C%20my%20curls%20are%20left%20with%20little%20to%20no%20flyaways.%20I%20would%20suggest%20pairing%20Laifen's%20diffuser%20attachment%20with%20their%20Hair%20Dryer%20Swift%20SE%2C%20an%20ionic%20blow%20dryer%20with%20200%20million%20negative%20ions%20for%20optimal%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20wavy%20hair%3Cp%3EWashing%20and%20drying%20wavy%20hair%20can%20be%20tricky%20because%20wavy%20hair%20strands%20are%20easily%20weighed%20down%20by%20water.%20Some%20people%20with%20loosely%20shaped%20waves%20might%20even%20experience%20their%20hair%20drying%20straight%2C%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20curl%20pattern.%20That's%20why%20it's%20essential%20to%20use%20a%20diffuser%20that%20will%20tactfully%20enhance%20definition%20and%20form%20voluminous%20waves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Curlsmith%20De-Frizzion%20Dryer's%20deep-reaching%20prongs%20gently%20support%20wavy%20hair%20strands%20while%20drying%20from%20tip%20to%20root%2C%20encouraging%20the%20formation%20of%20bouncy%20ringlets.%20For%20undeniably%20defined%20waves%2C%20we%20would%20suggest%20filling%20each%20section%20of%20hair%20into%20the%20diffuser%20bowl%20and%20bringing%20the%20bowl%20close%20to%20your%20scalp%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20Keep%20repeating%20this%20motion%20until%20your%20entire%20head%20of%20hair%20is%20dry%2C%20and%20you'll%20notice%20stunning%20waves%20beginning%20to%20take%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20splurge%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20healthy%20hair%20is%20essential%2C%20and%20although%20you%20can%20get%20away%20with%20purchasing%20cheap%20beauty%20tools%20that%20will%20do%20the%20trick%2C%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20spend%20a%20pretty%20penny.%20Yes%2C%20the%20Zuvi%20dryer%20with%20a%20diffuser%20costs%20almost%20%24350%2C%20but%20let%20us%20explain%20why%20it%20is%20the%20best%20diffuser%20for%20curly%20hair%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20splurge.%20Zuvi's%20Halo%20Hair%20Dryer%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20sizable%20diffuser%20attachment%20featuring%20eighteen%20prongs%2C%20uses%20a%20combination%20of%20infrared%20light%2C%20high-speed%20air%2C%20and%20cooler%20temperatures%20to%20define%20curls%20and%20reduce%20frizz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20unconventional%20method%2C%20which%20Zuvi%20calls%20their%20LightCare%20technology%2C%20is%20so%20unique%20because%20it%20dries%20water%20droplets%20on%20the%20hair's%20surface%20while%20leaving%20the%20internal%20moisture%20within%20your%20hairshaft%20undisturbed.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20process%20is%20intended%20to%20mimic%20the%20natural%20evaporation%20of%20sunshine%20and%20wind.%20For%20those%20struggling%20with%20damaged%20hair%20or%20sensitive%20scalps%2C%20or%20if%20you%20simply%20want%20a%20healthy%20alternative%20to%20beauty%20tools%20that%20use%20aggressive%20heat%2C%20we'd%20recommend%20using%20this%20diffuser%20to%20protect%20and%20rejuvenate%20your%20curls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20a%20diffuser%20is%20important%20for%20curly%20hair%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20buy%20an%20entirely%20new%20beauty%20tool.%20If%20you%20already%20own%20a%20hair%20dryer%2C%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20purchase%20a%20diffuser%20attachment%20that%20aligns%20with%20the%20size%20of%20your%20dryer.%20Conair's%20Volumizing%20Hair%20Diffuser%20is%20sold%20between%20%2410%20and%20%2413%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20retailer%2C%20and%20can%20fit%20any%20hair%20dryer%20between%201.8%20to%202.3%20inches.%20In%20addition%20to%20not%20breaking%20the%20bank%2C%20this%20diffuser%20is%20substantial%20concerning%20quality.%20The%20prongs%20attached%20to%20Conair's%20Diffuser%20are%20designed%20to%20lift%20and%20dry%20hair%20gently%20to%20mold%20perfectly%20defined%20curls.%20Reviewers%20also%20love%20that%20the%20diffuser%20attachment%20cups%20each%20curl%20nicely%20while%20enhancing%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20if%20your%20hair%20dryer%20is%20incompatible%20with%20the%20Conair%20Volumizing%20Hair%20Diffuser%20(i.e.%20if%20it's%20less%20than%201.8%20inches%20or%20more%20than%202.3%20inches)%2C%20plenty%20of%20diffuser%20attachments%20come%20in%20various%20sizes%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20tight%20curls%3Cp%3ECurly%20hair%20is%20not%20one-dimensional%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20types%2C%20patterns%2C%20and%20textures%20that%20exist.%20This%20means%20that%20not%20every%20product%20or%20tool%20will%20work%20universally%20across%20curly%20hair%2C%20and%20as%20someone%20with%20tight%20curls%2C%20finding%20the%20right%20products%20for%20my%20coils%20can%20be%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETight%20