jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68364924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20of%20Russian%20shortages%20come%20as%20concerns%20over%20the%20provision%20of%20Western%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine%20mount.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68364924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68364924.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68364924.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20Say%20Won't%20March%20To%20Delhi%20For%202%20Days%2C%201%20Dies%20During%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%20has%20died%20at%20Haryana's%20Khanauri%20border%2C%20where%20protesting%20farmers%20clashed%20with%20the%20police%20this%20evening.%20Farmers'%20group%20AIKS%20(All-India%20Kisan%20Sabha)%20alleged%20he%20died%20during%20the%20police%20action%2C%20which%20the%20Haryana%20police%20have%20denied.%20The%20farmers%20have%20also%20suspended%20their%20protest%20march%20to%20Delhi%20for%20two%20days%2C%20though%20the%20sit-in%20protest%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20at%20a%20Patiala%20hospital%20where%20Shubh%20Karan%20Singh%20was%20taken%2C%20said%20he%20had%20sustained%20a%20bullet%20wound.%20A%20post-mortem%20is%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20patients%20have%20come%20to%20us%20from%20Khanauri.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20dead%20on%20arrival%2C%20the%20other%20two%20are%20stable%20and%20seem%20to%20have%20sustained%20bullet%20injuries...%20but%20it%20can't%20be%20confirmed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Rekhi%2C%20the%20Senior%20Medical%20Officer%20of%20Patiala's%20Rajendra%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20person%20who%20was%20dead%20on%20arrival%20had%20a%20bullet%20injury%20on%20his%20head%2C%20but%20more%20details%20such%20as%20size%20of%20the%20bullet%20can%20only%20be%20confirmed%20after%20postmortem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20Police%20had%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20the%20advancing%20farmers%20to%20thwart%20their%20attempts%20to%20breach%20the%20barricades%20at%20the%20border%2C%20the%20farmers%20said.%20The%20march%20was%20continuing%20after%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20rejected%20a%20proposal%20made%20by%20the%20government%20yesterday.%20It%20was%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks%20to%20break%20the%20deadlock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20Police%20have%20denied%20any%20death.%20A%20post%20from%20the%20police%20handle%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20information%20received%20so%20far%2C%20no%20farmer%20has%20died%20today...%20This%20is%20just%20a%20rumour.%20There%20is%20information%20about%20two%20policemen%20and%20one%20protestor%20being%20injured%20at%20Data%20Singh-Khanori%20border%20who%20is%20undergoing%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20confirmed%20the%20death.%20Describing%20how%20he%20was%20acting%20as%20the%20interlocuter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20I%20came%20to%20know%20and%20saw%20the%20video%2C%20I%20got%20goosebumps%2C%20I%20felt%20very%20sad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%2C%20two%20farmer%20groups%20issued%20angry%20statements%2C%20blaming%20the%20state%20police%20and%20the%20Central%20government.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubh%20Karan%20Singh's%20death%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20police%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20AIKS.%20%26quot%3BThis%20killing%20exposes%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20even%20while%20claiming%20to%20be%20'farmer-friendly'.%20The%20BJP%20government%20in%20Haryana%20led%20by%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20is%20treating%20protesting%20farmers%E2%80%94who%20are%20marching%20towards%20Delhi%E2%80%94%20like%20enemy%20soldiers%20and%20is%20carrying%20out%20war-like%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Executive%20that%20failed%20to%20implement%20the%20agreement%20with%20SKM%20signed%20on%209th%20December%202021%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20present%20crisis%20and%20the%20causality%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20or%20SKM.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubh%20Karan%20Singh%2C%2023%2C%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Bathinda.%20He%20was%20the%20son%20of%20Charanjit%20Singh%2C%20residents%20of%20village%20Valo%20in%20Bathinda%20district%2C%20said%20farmer%20leader%20Kaka%20Singh%20Kotra.%20His%20body%20has%20been%20kept%20at%20the%20Rajendra%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20farmer%2C%20Mr%20Mann%20said%2C%20was%20the%20owner%20of%202%20acres.%20His%20mother%20died%20early%20and%20he%20was%20raised%20by%20his%20grandmother.%20He%20had%20two%20sisters.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20he%20need%20to%20go%20there%3F%20He%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%2C%20why%20did%20he%20have%20to%20stay%20at%20Khanauri%20or%20Shambhu%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20have%20been%20protesting%20with%20a%20series%20of%20demands%2C%20which%20include%20enactment%20of%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20for%20all%20crops%2C%20farmer%20loan%20waiver%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20round%20of%20talks%2C%20which%20ended%20past%20midnight%20Sunday%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20Union%20ministers%20had%20proposed%20buying%20five%20crops%20--%20moong%20dal%2C%20urad%20dal%2C%20tur%20dal%2C%20maize%20and%20cotton%20--%20from%20farmers%20at%20minimum%20support%20price%20for%20five%20years%20through%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Anurag