3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fexpensive-acquisitions-of-virat-kohli-and-anushka-sharma%2Fphotostory%2F107892781.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sugarcane%20Fair%20Price%20Hiked%20Amid%20Protests%2C%20Minister%20Says%20%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20Pro-Farmer%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20sugarcane%20has%20been%20increased%20by%208%20per%20cent%20for%20the%202024-25%20financial%20year%20and%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20October%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%20The%20hike%20came%20amid%20a%20huge%20tussle%20between%20the%20government%20and%20farmers%20over%20minimum%20support%20price.%20The%20price%20of%20cane%20will%20now%20go%20up%20from%20Rs%20315%20to%20Rs%20340%20a%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20hike%2C%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20declared%20that%20the%20government%20is%20pro-farmer.%20%26quot%3BOur%20government%20is%20working%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20farmers%20and%20agriculture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20fix%20the%20price%20for%20the%20upcoming%20sugarcane%20season%2C%20in%20the%20period%20from%20October%201%2C%202024%2C%20to%20September%2030%2C%202025%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20fair%20and%20reasonable%20price%20of%20sugarcane%20to%20the%20farmers%20by%20the%20sugar%20mills%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20fix%20the%20price%20at%20Rs%20340%20per%20quintal%20for%20the%20year%202024-25%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%20which%20was%20Rs%20315%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cabinet%20approval%20for%20the%20cane%20price%20hike%20came%20this%20evening%20during%20a%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BFair%20and%20Remunerative%20Price%26quot%3B%20will%20ensure%20prosperity%20of%20sugarcane%20farmers%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20government%20said%20it%20has%20provided%20a%20premium%20of%20Rs.%203.32%20per%20quintal%20for%20every%200.1%20percentage%20point%20increase%20above%2010.25%25%20in%20the%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20India%20is%20already%20paying%20the%20highest%20price%20of%20sugarcane%20in%20the%20world%20and%20despite%20that%2C%20the%C2%A0%20government%20is%20ensuring%20the%20world's%20cheapest%20sugar%20to%20domestic%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20decision%20will%20benefit%20more%20than%205%20crore%20sugarcane%20farmers%20and%20their%20families%20and%20lakhs%20of%20other%20persons%20involved%20in%20sugar%20sector%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20re-confirms%20fulfilment%20of%20Modi%20ki%20Guarantee%20to%20double%20farmers'%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708541700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fggcjispg_anurag-thakur-pti_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugarcane-fair-price-hiked-amid-protests-union-minister-anurag-thakur-says-we-are-pro-farmer-5102656%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20price%20of%20sugarcane%20has%20been%20increased%20by%208%20per%20cent%20for%20the%202024-25%20financial%20year%20and%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20October%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugarcane-fair-price-hiked-amid-protests-union-minister-anurag-thakur-says-we-are-pro-farmer-5102656%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugarcane-fair-price-hiked-amid-protests-union-minister-anurag-thakur-says-we-are-pro-farmer-5102656%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22am