%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20moon%20lander%20built%20by%20Houston-based%20company%20Intuitive%20Machines%20reached%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20headed%20for%20an%20attempt%20at%20the%20first%20US%20touchdown%20on%20Earth's%20nearest%20celestial%20neighbour%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20and%20the%20first%20ever%20by%20a%20private%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-legged%20Nova-C%20lander%2C%20dubbed%20Odysseus%2C%20entered%20a%20circular%20orbit%2057%20miles%20(92%20km)%20above%20the%20lunar%20surface%20after%20firing%20its%20main%20rocket%20thruster%20for%20nearly%20seven%20minutes%20in%20an%20orbital%20insertion%20manoeuvre%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20an%20online%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssuming%20all%20goes%20according%20to%20plan%2C%20the%20robot%20spacecraft%20is%20expected%20to%20gradually%20lower%20its%20orbit%20over%20the%20next%2024%20hours%20and%20land%20at%20crater%20Malapert%20A%20near%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20at%205%3A49%20p.m.%20EST%20(2249%20GMT)%20on%20Thursday%2C%20carrying%20a%20suite%20of%20NASA%20science%20instruments%20and%20technology%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdysseus%20was%20launched%20six%20days%20ago%2C%20on%20Feb.%2015%2C%20atop%20a%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20built%20and%20flown%20by%20Elon%20Musk's%20California-based%20company%20SpaceX%20from%20NASA's%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20in%20Cape%20Canaveral%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20landing%20succeeds%2C%20the%20IM-1%20mission%20would%20represent%20the%20first%20controlled%20descent%20to%20the%20lunar%20surface%20by%20a%20U.S.%20spacecraft%20since%20Apollo%2017%2C%20when%20NASA's%20last%20crewed%20moon%20mission%20carried%20Gene%20Cernan%20and%20Harrison%20Schmitt%20landed%20there%20in%201972.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20would%20mark%20the%20first%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20landing%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20moon%20ever%20by%20a%20commercially%20manufactured%20and%20operated%20vehicle%20and%20the%20first%20under%20NASA's%20Artemis%20lunar%20program%2C%20as%20the%20U.S.%20races%20to%20return%20astronauts%20to%20Earth's%20natural%20satellite%20before%20China%20lands%20its%20own%20crewed%20spacecraft%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IM-1%20mission%20comes%20about%20a%20month%20after%20the%20lunar%20lander%20of%20another%20firm%2C%20Astrobotic%20Technology%2C%20suffered%20a%20propulsion%20system%20leak%20on%20its%20way%20to%20the%20moon%20shortly%20after%20being%20placed%20in%20orbit%20on%20Jan.%208%20by%20a%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%20(ULA)%20Vulcan%20rocket%20making%20its%20debut%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20malfunction%20of%20Astrobotic's%20Peregrine%20lander%2C%20which%20was%20also%20flying%20NASA%20payloads%20to%20the%20moon%2C%20was%20the%20third%20time%20a%20private%20company%20had%20failed%20to%20achieve%20a%20lunar%20touchdown%2C%20following%20ill-fated%20efforts%20by%20companies%20from%20Israel%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20mishaps%20illustrated%20the%20risks%20NASA%20faces%20in%20leaning%20more%20heavily%20on%20the%20commercial%20sector%20than%20it%20had%20in%20the%20past%20to%20realize%20its%20spaceflight%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20considered%20an%20Intuitive%20Machines%20mission%2C%20the%20IM-1%20flight%20is%20carrying%20six%20NASA%20payloads%20of%20instruments%20designed%20to%20gather%20data%20about%20the%20lunar%20environment%20ahead%20of%20NASA's%20planned%20first%20crewed%20Artemis%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%20later%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20announced%20last%20month%20that%20it%20was%20delaying%20its%20target%20date%20for%20the%20first%20crewed%20Artemis%20moon%20landing%20from%202025%20to%20late%202026%2C%20while%20China%20has%20said%20it%20was%20aiming%20for%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmall%20landers%20such%20as%20Nova-C%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20there%20first%2C%20carrying%20instruments%20to%20closely%20survey%20the%20lunar%20landscape%2C%20its%20resources%20and%20potential%20hazards.%20Odysseus%20will%20focus%20on%20space%20weather%20interactions%20with%20the%20moon's%20surface%2C%20radio%20astronomy%2C%20precision%20landing%20technologies%20and%20navigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20spacecraft%20from%20just%20five%20countries%20have%20ever%20landed%20on%20the%20moon%20-%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20China%2C%20India%20and%2C%20most%20recently%20just%20last%20month%2C%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708537500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Feqqqbebo_novac-lander-_625x300_21_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-moon-lander-enters-orbit-for-1st-us-lunar-touchdown-in-50-years-5102396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20moon%20lander%20built%20by%20Houston-based%20company%20Intuitive%20Machines%20reached%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20headed%20for%20an%20attempt%20at%20the%20first%20US%20touchdown%20on%20Earth's%20nearest%20celestial%20neighbour%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-moon-lander-enters-orbit-for-1st-us-lunar-touchdown-in-50-years-5102396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-moon-lander-enters-orbit-for-1st-us-lunar-touchdown-in-50-years-5102396%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-moon-lander-enters-orbit-for-1st-us-lunar-touchdown-in-50-years-5102396%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Second%20IIPS%20Student%20Arrested%20For%20Allegedly%20Posting%20Against%20Celebration%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20Ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084846%2FIIPS.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Govandi%20police%20station%20in%20Mumbai%20has%20arrested%20a%2025-year-old%20student%20of%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences%20(IIPS)%20for%20allegedly%20posting%20a%20story%20on%20WhatsApp%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20arrest%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20student%2C%20who%20had%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20of%20this%20student%E2%80%99s%20post%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20on%20January%2022%20and%20released%20on%20bail%20after%20two%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20classmates%2C%20the%20police%20reached%20the%20IIPS%20campus%20early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2021%20and%20arrested%20him%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20contacted%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20director%20Dr%20S.K.%20Singh%20as%20well%20as%20its%20chief%20administrator%20and%20registrar%20Prashant%20Borde%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorde%2C%20who%20reportedly%20permitted%20the%20police%20to%20enter%20the%20campus%20and%20arrest%20the%20students%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20was%20in%20a%20hospital%20and%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20this%20reporter%20should%20visit%20the%20IIPS%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%2C%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20question%20about%20the%20arrest%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20visit%20the%20IIPS%20tomorrow%20to%20find%20the%20facts%20rather%20than%20promoting%C2%A0a%20false%C2%A0narrative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20reporter%20asked%20if%20the%20information%20about%20the%20arrest%20was%20not%20a%20fact%2C%20Singh%20didn%E2%80%99t%20clarify.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%202%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20about%20the%20frenzy%20that%20broke%20out%20on%20the%20IIPS%20campus%20following%20the%20celebrations%20carried%20out%20by%20right-leaning%20students%20in%20the%20institute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20group%20of%20students%2C%20mostly%20belonging%20to%20Bahujan%20communities%2C%20had%20submitted%20a%20letter%20to%20Singh%20pointing%20to%20problem%20behind%20allowing%20the%20celebration%20on%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmumbai-student-arrested-after-asking-admin-to-curb-ram-temple-celebrations-on-campus%5C%22%3EMumbai%3A%20Student%20Arrested%20After%20Asking%20Admin%20to%20Curb%20Ram%20Temple%20Celebrations%20on%20Campus%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20claim%2C%20was%20confidential%20and%20signed%20by%20at%20least%2035%20of%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20institute%20failed%20to%20intervene%20and%20offer%20any%20solution%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20students%2C%20the%20letter%20was%20leaked%20and%20soon%20reached%20right-wing%20activists%20both%20on%20and%20outside%20campus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20signatories%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20student%20belonging%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20was%20the%20first%20one%20to%20be%20arrested.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20invoked%20sections%20153(A)%20and%20295(A)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20him%2C%20which%20deal%20with%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%20and%20outraging%20religious%20feelings%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20student%20had%20allegedly%20only%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20post%20critical%20of%20the%20celebration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20discovered%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20post%20during%20its%20investigation%20and%20had%20summoned%20the%20other%20student%20for%20questioning%20multiple%20times.%20Originally%20from%20Kerala%2C%20this%20student%20had%20returned%20to%20his%20hometown%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20came%20back%20%5Bto%20the%20IIPS%20campus%5D%20since%20he%20had%20to%20take%20the%20viva%20voce%20exams%20and%20also%20submit%20his%20dissertation.%20The%20moment%20he%20returned%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20and%20classmates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20student%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Kerala%2C%20confirmed%20the%20news%20of%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20student%20will%20be%20produced%20before%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20February%2022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20letter%20to%20the%20director%2C%20the%20students%20had%20written%3A%20%E2%80%9CIIPS%20is%20a%20multicultural%20campus%20annually%20organising%20various%20celebrations%20which%20includes%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20Dussehra%2C%20Christmas%2C%20etc%20which%20epitomises%20the%20promise%20of%20grooming%20a%20secular%20young%20generation%20who%20can%20contribute%20prosperity%20to%20a%20diversified%20nation-state%20like%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20celebration%20of%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20a%20pure%20act%20of%20political%20agenda%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20various%20outfits%2C%20which%20can%20harm%20the%20secular%20sentiments%20of%20students%20while%20celebrating%20in%20an%20institute%20like%20IIPS%2C%20where%20such%20celebrations%20cannot%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20students%20sought%20restrictions%20on%20celebrations%20on%20campus%20and%20said%20the%20celebration%20in%20question%20had%20the%20potential%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20deepening%20the%20divisions%20among%20%5Bthe%5D%20student%20fraternity%20by%20spreading%20hate%20and%20fear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20letter%20was%20leaked%2C%20the%20students%20claimed%20they%20were%20bullied%20into%20submitting%20an%20apology%20for%20%E2%80%9Churting%20%5Bthe%5D%20sentiments%20of%20those%20celebrating%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708537334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02084846%2FIIPS.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcampus%2Fsecond-iips-student-arrested-posting-against-ram-temple-celebration%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20classmates%2C%20the%20police%20reached%20the%20IIPS%20campus%20early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2021%20and%20arrested%20him%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcampus%2Fsecond-iips-student-arrested-posting-against-ram-temple-celebration%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cabinet%20clears%20hike%20in%20sugarcane%20FRP%20by%20Rs%2025%20to%20Rs%20340%20per%20quintal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708536569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-03%2F04%2Ffull%2F1457078308-4985.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fagriculture%2Fcabinet-clears-hike-in-sugarcane-frp-by-rs-25-to-rs-340-per-quintal-124