%3EAramane%20was%20asked%20about%20challenges%20India%20is%20facing%20along%20the%20LAC%20and%20New%20Delhi's%20expectations%20from%20Washington%20to%20deal%20with%20common%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20which%20helped%20us%20very%20quickly%20is%20the%20intelligence%2C%20the%20situational%20awareness%20which%20the%20US%20equipment%20and%20the%20US%20government%20helped%20us%20with.%20So%20that%20is%20one%20single%20most%20important%20area%20...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20secretary%20said%20the%20strong%20resolve%20that%20both%20India%20and%20the%20US%20support%20each%20other%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20common%20threat%20is%20going%20to%20be%20of%20critical%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20giving%20a%20face-off%20to%20our%20neighbour%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20fronts%20we%20have%20with%20them%2C%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20mountain%20pass%2C%20we%20are%20stationed%20there...%20and%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20road%20we%20have%20to%20be%20there.%20So%20that%20way%20we%20are%20there%20standing%20against%20a%20bully%20in%20a%20very%20determined%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Aramane%20said%20India%20expects%20friends%20like%20the%20US%20to%20be%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20that%20our%20friends%20in%20the%20US%20will%20be%20there%20with%20us%20in%20case%20we%20need%20their%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20greatly%20appreciate%20the%20support%20and%20resolve%20from%20our%20friends%20in%20supporting%20us%20during%20such%20an%20event%2C%20basically%20the%20information%2C%20the%20intelligence%20and%20any%20support%20by%20way%20of%20equipment%20will%20be%20of%20great%20use%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20standoff%20in%20certain%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20even%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20disengagement%20from%20several%20areas%20following%20extensive%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Aramane%20stressed%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20are%20key%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20bounded%20by%20shared%20values%20and%20common%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20The%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20with%20its%20vast%20expanse%20of%20oceans%20and%20strategic%20waterways%2C%20stands%20as%20the%20crossroad%20of%20global%20commerce%2C%20geopolitics%2C%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Aramane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20navigating%20the%20complex%20dynamics%20of%20this%20region%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20find%20themselves%20as%20key%20stakeholders%2C%20bound%20by%20shared%20values%20and%20common%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20robust%20defence%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20rooted%20in%20mutual%20respect%20and%20strategic%20convergence%2C%20Aramane%20also%20cited%20the%20launch%20of%20Initiatives%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technologies%20(iCET)%20as%20a%20key%20measure%20to%20bolster%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pivotal%20aspect%20of%20our%20burgeoning%20relationship%20is%20the%20iCET%20that%20aims%20to%20establish%20'Innovation%20Bridges'%20across%20key%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bilateral%20partnership%20in%20the%20aerospace%20and%20defence%20sectors%2C%20Aramane%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20bilateral%20relationship%20is%20flourishing%2C%20with%20India%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20the%20US%20for%20cutting-edge%20equipment%20and%20technology.%20The%20US%20in%20turn%2C%20sees%20India%20as%20a%20key%20partner%20in%20its%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%2C%20leveraging%20India's%20growing%20defence%20capabilities.%26q