%3Fv%3Dv_eoKFcQ4Yo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%20%26quot%3BSarfaraz%20had%20to%20walk%20off%20at%2062%2C%20his%20first-ever%20Test%20match.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20dismissal%20at%20the%20end%20of%20day's%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%20there%20is%20miscommunication%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Sometimes%20you%20get%20run%20out.%20Such%20kind%20of%20things%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20%C2%A0said%20in%20the%20post-match%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20added%20that%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20helped%20him%20throughout%20his%20innings.%20%26quot%3BI%20talked%20to%20him%20at%20lunch%20time.%20I%20am%20that%20type%20of%20batter%20who%20like%20to%20talk%20while%20batting%20about%20what%20is%20going%20on.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20Jadeja%20to%20keep%20talking%20to%20me%20while%20I%20bat.%20He%20supported%20me%20a%20lot%20today%20and%20spoke%20to%20me%20at%20lunchtime%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20how%20the%20debutants%20feel%20and%20how%20he%20felt%20as%20a%20debutant.%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20nervous%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20played%20my%20first%20sweep%20and%20missed%20it.%20But%20he%20told%20me%20to%20take%20some%20time%20and%20it%20would%20be%20easy.%20I%20listened%20to%20him%20and%20tried%20implementing%20it.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20Jadeja%20said%20on%20the%20run%20out%2C%20Sarfaraz%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20miscommunication%2C%20but%20I%20said%20it's%20okay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708534500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0en0p688_sarfaraz-khan_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fravindra-jadeja-the-guilty-party-ab-de-villiers-clear-verdict-on-sarfaraz-khan-run-out-5102101%22%