%20like%20the%20Trinity%2C%26quot%3B%20Branciani%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20central%20Christian%20doctrine%20of%20three%20persons%20within%20one%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupnik%20was%20briefly%20excommunicated%20in%202020%20for%20absolving%20someone%20of%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20him%2C%20but%20was%20reinstated%20after%20he%20formally%20repented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20finally%20expelled%20from%20the%20Jesuit%20order%20--%20of%20which%20Pope%20Francis%20is%20a%20member%20--%20last%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Francis%20waived%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations%20on%20the%20offences%2C%20opening%20the%20way%20for%20potential%20disciplinary%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnne%20Barrett%20Doyle%2C%20co-director%20of%20the%20abuse%20tracking%20site%20Bishop%20Accountability%2C%20which%20documents%20abuse%20within%20the%20Catholic%20Church%2C%20described%20Rupnik%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20cleric%20who%20was%20protected%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20Church%20and%20the%20Vatican.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20conference%20comes%20five%20years%20after%20an%20unprecedented%20summit%20at%20the%20Vatican%20on%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20the%20Church%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20which%20Francis%20promised%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero%20tolerance%26quot%3B%20approached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Rupnik%20case%20shows%20that%20little%20has%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrett%20Doyle%2C%20who%20called%20for%20an%20independent%20investigation%20and%20the%20publication%20of%20its%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708533780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fm8hhhr0c_slovenia-nuns-afp_625x300_21_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fex-nuns-on-renowned-priest-in-