t%2Farticleshow%2F107891042.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Paper%20Leak%20'Kingpins'%20Made%20Crores%2C%20But%20Money%20Wasn't%20Only%20Motive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20for%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20investigating%20the%20paper%20leak%20cases%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20four%20suspected%20kingpins%20of%20the%20racket%20have%20been%20arrested.%20The%20arrests%20have%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20four%20men%2C%20who%20are%20government%20employees%20themselves%2C%20was%20not%20just%20to%20make%20money%20-%20which%20they%20did%20by%20the%20bucketload%20-%20but%20also%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20relatives%20got%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20there%20have%20been%20seven%20high-profile%20exams%20in%20which%20papers%20were%20leaked%20and%20the%20issue%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Congress%20government's%20loss%20in%20the%20state%20in%20last%20year's%20elections.%20The%20four%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Junior%20Engineer%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20December%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20accused%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20are%20Harshwardhan%20Meena%2C%20who%20is%20a%20revenue%20official%2C%20Rajendra%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20a%20government%20teacher%2C%20Shivratan%20Mot%2C%20a%20librarian%20and%C2%A0Rajendra%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20alias%20Raju%2C%20a%20police%20sub-inspector.%20The%20police%20said%20they%20suspect%20that%20the%20four%20men%20worked%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20cheating%20rings%20operating%20in%20the%20state%20and%20were%20among%20the%20kingpins%20of%20the%20paper%20leak%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20believe%20Meena%20did%20not%20only%20make%20crores%20from%20leaking%20papers%20but%20that%20he%20and%20his%20family%20were%20involved%20in%20getting%20dummy%20candidates%20appear%20for%20the%20exams.%20Like%20Meena%2C%20his%20wife%20is%20also%20a%20revenue%20official%2C%20and%20she%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20made%20a%20dummy%20candidate%20sit%20for%20a%20police%20sub-inspector%20exam.%20She%20had%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20the%20physical%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeena's%20brother%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20earlier%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20dummy%20candidate%20for%20the%20senior%20teacher%20exam%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20a%20government%20school%20teacher%2C%20was%20part%20of%20conducting%20the%20junior%20engineer%20exam%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20paper%20leak.%20He%20was%20the%20one%20who%20allegedly%20took%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20paper%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20Meena%20for%20Rs%2050%20lakh.%20Meena%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20made%20crores%20from%20selling%20it%20to%20interested%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20Yadav%20ensured%20that%20his%20son%20became%20a%20junior%20engineer%2C%20and%20his%20daughter-in-law%20is%20also%20a%20senior%20government%20teacher%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVK%20Singh%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Special%20Operations%20Group%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHarshwardhan%20Meena%20was%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20Nepal%20border.%20The%20groups%20linked%20to%20cheating%20and%20leaking%20of%20papers%20in%20the%20state%20sometimes%20cooperate%20and%2C%20at%20other%20times%2C%20they%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20four%20men%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20the%20role%20of%2050%20government%20employees%20from%20various%20departments%20is%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708530840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fb7m6hfb8_jen-paper-leak-accused_625x300_20_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-paper-leak-kingpins-made-crores-but-money-wasnt