0trying%20to%20foment%20trouble%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20house%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20ration%20scam%20on%20January%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708528080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0qlpkdl4_sandeshkhali_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconscience-shocked-human-rights-panel-to-send-team-to-sandeshkhali-5101165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20as%20the%20politics%20surrounding%20the%20issue%20continues%20to%20heat%20up%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20rape%20levelled%20against%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20strongman%20and%20his%20aides%20by%20women%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconscience-shocked-human-rights-panel-to-send-team-to-sandeshkhali-5101165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconscience-shocked-human-rights-panel-to-send-team-to-sandeshkhali-5101165%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconscience-shocked-human-rights-panel-to-send-team-to-sandeshkhali-5101165%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HSBC%20posts%2025%25%20rise%20in%20profit%20from%20India%20operations%20to%20%241.5%20bn%20in%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708527867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-05%2F04%2Ffull%2F1525410682-0349.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhsbc-posts-25-rise-in-profit-from-india-operations-to-1-5-bn-in-2023-124022100996_1.html