%3EHad%20Keskar%2C%20the%20first%20Indian%20information%20and%20broadcasting%20minister%20and%20a%20high-minded%20purist%2C%20not%20banned%20film%20music%20from%20All%20India%20Radio%20(AIR)%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20started%20his%20most%20famous%20programme%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBinaca%20Geetmala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20upset%20film%20producers%20and%20record%20companies%2C%20who%20needed%20to%20publicise%20their%20songs%2C%20on%20which%20the%20success%20of%20movies%20often%20depended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadio%20Ceylon%20stepped%20into%20the%20breach.%20Using%20a%20powerful%20short-wave%20transmitter%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20Americans%20in%20Ceylon%2C%20the%20radio%20station%20started%20beaming%20out%20of%20programmes%20to%20India%20and%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGenerations%20of%20Indians%20grew%20up%20listening%20to%20his%20voice%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBinaca%20Geetmala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20named%20after%20a%20toothpaste%20brand%20%E2%80%93%20every%20Wednesday%20at%208%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20it%2C%20Sayani%20listed%2016%20songs%20in%20the%20order%20of%20popularity%2C%20the%20final%20one%20being%20introduced%20with%20a%20bugle%2C%20or%20in%20his%20words%2C%20with%20a%20Bigul.%20His%20sweet%20voice%20and%20warm%2C%20friendly%20tone%20endeared%20him%20to%20millions%20and%20his%20pet%20phrases%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebehnon%20aur%20bhaiyon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(sisters%20and%20brothers)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaur%20ab%20agli%20badaan%20par%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(on%20the%20next%20step)%2C%20became%20wildly%20popular%2C%20or%20went%20viral%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20language.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20list%20was%20prepared%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20postcards%20received%20from%20listeners%20%E2%80%93%20there%20were%20often%20reports%20of%20mass%20postcards%20being%20sent%20by%20producers%20themselves%2C%20which%20Sayani%20had%20to%20discard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20responses%20came%20from%20every%20part%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20he%20often%20picked%20out%20the%20odd%20postcard%20and%20read%20them%20out%2C%20and%20listeners%20became%20very%20familiar%20with%20names%20they%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20before%2C%20such%20as%20Jhumri%20Talaiya%20and%20Rajnandgaon%2C%20which%20are%20now%20memes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESayani%20came%20into%20commercial%20broadcasting%20thanks%20to%20his%20elder%20brother%20Hamid%2C%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20show%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBinaca%20Hit%20Parade%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20played%20western%20music.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21200349%2FBrothers.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22616%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21200349%2FBrothers.jpg%20616w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21200349%2FBrothers-285x300.jpg%20285w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698241%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHamid%20and%20Ameen%20Sayani%20during%20a%20recording.%20Photo%3A%20Rajil%20Sayani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamid%E2%80%99s%20programme%20was%20popular%20with%20Indians%20starved%20for%20songs%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Frank%20Sinatra%20and%20Dean%20Martin%20and%20he%20convinced%20Binaca%20to%20give%20the%20young%20Ameen%20the%20Hindi%20version.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20good%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20clear%20communications%20skills%20and%20use%20of%20simple%20Hindustani%20came%20from%20his%20mother%20Kulsum%20Sayani%2C%20who%20was%20told%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20in%201940%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20magazine%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Urdu%20and%20Gujarati%20written%20in%20simple%20language%20for%20neo-literates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20initially%20recorded%20the%20programme%20in%20a%20room%20in%20St%20Xavier%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20Ameen%20had%20studied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadio%20Ceylon%20had%20several%20other%20programmes%2C%20run%20by%20Gopal%20Sharma%20and%20another%20enthusiastic%20young%20man%2C%20Balraj%20Dutt%2C%20who%20interviewed%20film%20stars.%20Dutt%20soon%20got%20a%20film%20role%20and%20changed%20his%20name%20to%20Sunil%20Dutt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20Binaca-sponsored%20programmes%20ran%20concurrently.%20In%201975%2C%20Hamid%20Sayani%20passed%20away%20and%20his%20brother%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20that%20too%2C%20before%20it%20was%20phased%20out%20three%20years%20later.%20But%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBinaca%20Geetmala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20like%20its%20voice%2C%20was%20indefatigable%20%E2%80%93%20it%20continued%20till%201994%2C%20a%20record%20run%20of%2042%20years!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21201414%2FBachchan.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22852%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21201414%2FBachchan.jpg%20852w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21201414%2FBachchan-300x187.jpg%20300w%5C%