%3A%22Escape%20Route%2C%20Alarm%20Systems%20Absent%20in%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%3A%20Expert%20Panel%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20collapse%20where%2041%20workers%20were%20trapped%20for%2017%20days%20in%20November%2C%20an%20expert%20panel%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20underlined%20that%20there%20was%20an%20absence%20of%20an%20escape%20route%20and%20alarm%20systems%20in%20the%20structure%20and%20pointed%20out%20other%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20planning%20and%20designing%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonths-after-uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-panel-flags-shortcomings-in-planning-101708424967605.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20escape%20route%20and%20an%20alarm%20system%20in%20case%20of%20tragedy.%20Even%20monitoring%20was%20not%20proper%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shantanu%20Sarkar%2C%20director%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Landslide%20Mitigation%20and%20Management%20Centre%2C%20who%20led%20the%20six-member%20expert%20committee%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20underlined%20that%20the%20design%20report%20%E2%80%9Clacked%20detailed%20geotechnical%20and%20geophysical%20investigations%E2%80%9D.%20Further%2C%20the%2070-page%20report%20called%20for%20a%20detailed%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20adding%20that%20safety%20should%20never%20be%20compromised%20to%20meet%20completion%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConducting%20more%20exploratory%20bore-holes%20and%20geophysical%20investigations%20can%20identify%20critical%20geological%20features%20and%20minimise%20risks%20during%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-one%20workers%20were%20trapped%20for%2017%20days%20in%20the%20collapsed%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarkashi%20after%20it%20collapsed.%20They%20were%20pulled%20out%20after%20manual%20digging%20for%20over%2026%20hours%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20primitive%20rat-hole%20mining%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20key%20highlights%20of%20the%20report%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CPGmhKLdu4QDFVmKZgIdduUMwA%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManual%20monitoring%2C%20conducted%20periodically%2C%20may%20not%20provide%20timely%20insights%20into%20evolving%20situations.%20Shifting%20towards%20real-time%20monitoring%20can%20offer%20proactive%20responses%20to%20dynamic%20conditions%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImplementing%20an%20evacuation%20plan%2C%20such%20as%20installing%20concrete%20hume%20pipes%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20facilitate%20quick%20evacuation%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20collapse%20tragedy.%20Incorporating%20an%20alarm%20system%20for%20evacuation%20is%20essential%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20works%E2%80%A6.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20panel%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcollapses-during-silkyara-tunnel-construction-central-team%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9919-20%E2%80%B2%20Collapses%20During%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20Construction%20in%20Last%205%20Years%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecommendations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20panel%2C%20for%20a%20Silkyara-like%C2%A0project%20in%20the%20future%20comprehensive%20site%20study%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20assessing%20rock%20formations%2C%20seismic%20activity%2C%20and%20potential%20risks%20to%20ensure%20that%20tunnels%20are%20designed%20to%20withstand%20the%20geological%20challenges%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20report%20recommended%20formulation%20of%20project-specific%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20and%20proper%20training%20for%20workers.%C2%A0For%20tunnel%20collapses%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20that%20detailed%20and%20scenario-specific%20emergency%20plans%20should%20be%20formulated.%20It%20also%20underlined%20that%20design%20engineers%20should%20conduct%20regular%20inspections%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Cdeviations%20and%20implement%20corrective%20measures%20to%20deal%20with%20geological%20surprises%E2%80%9D%20and%20technical%20advisory%20committee%20should%20also%20be%20constituted%20to%20visit%20the%20tunnel%20at%20regular%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20regularly%20monitor%20similar%20projects%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20an%20interdepartmental%20coordination%20committee%20to%20be%20constituted%20at%20the%20national%2C%20state%2C%20and%20district%20levels.%C2%A0It%20also%20said%20a%20system%20should%20be%20established%20for%20monitoring%20the%20structural%20health%20of%20tunnels%20post-construction%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CLWrlKPdu4QDFb6VZgIdUPEKyA%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdhering%20to%20the%20prescribed%20rate%20of%20tunnel%20excavation%20is%20vital%20to%20maintaining%20stability%20and%20preventing%20unforeseen%20ground%20deformations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20report%20added%20that%20tunnels%20must%20be%20designed%20keeping%20seismic%20considerations%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20in%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20recommendations%20aim%20to%20address%20the%20gaps%20identified%20in%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20project%2C%20enhance%20safety%20measures%2C%20and%20inform%20future%20tunnel%20constructions%20in%20challenging%20geological%20conditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20National%20Highways%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20(NHIDCL)%2C%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99s%20executing%20agency%2C%20rejected%20the%20report.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20findings.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20into%20cognisance%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20NHIDCL%20director%20Anshu%20Manish%20Khalkho.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManual%20monitoring%2C%20conducted%20periodically%2C%20may%20not%20provide%20timely%20insights%20into%20evolving%20situations.%20Shifting%20towards%20real-time%20monitoring%20can%20offer%20proactive%20responses%20to%20dynamic%20conditions%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImplementing%20an%20evacuation%20plan%2C%20such%20as%20installing%20concrete%20hume%20pipes%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20facilitate%20quick%20evacuation%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20collapse%20tragedy.%20Incorporating%20an%20alarm%20system%20for%20evacuation%20is%20essential%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20works%E2%80%A6.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20panel%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708504249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fescape-route-alarm-systems-absent-in-silkyara-tunnel-in-uttarakhand-expert-panel-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20order%20to%20regularly%20monitor%20similar%20projects%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20panel%20suggested%20an%20interdepartmental%20coordination%20committee%20t