0have%20been%20no%20ifs%20or%20buts%20to%20the%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20pronouncement%20bodes%20well%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20once%20also%2C%20the%20verdict%20leaves%20no%20room%20for%20talk-backs.%20Nor%20does%20the%20Ordinance%20route%20seem%20to%20promise%20much%20respite%20for%20the%20powers-that-be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDates%20have%20been%20set%20for%20when%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20must%20convey%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20the%20names%20of%20bond-buyers%2C%20the%20dates%20and%20amounts%20of%20purchase%2C%20and%20the%20names%20of%20those%20benefited%20thereof%3B%20and%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20turn%20to%20communicate%20the%20gathered%20data%20on%20its%20website%20to%20the%20people%20who%20%E2%80%9Cgave%20to%20themselves%E2%80%9D%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20supremacy%20of%20the%20elector%E2%80%99s%2Fcitizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20information%20under%20Article%2019(1)%20(a)%20and%20via%20the%20RTI%20Act%20has%20been%20held%20to%20be%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20thus%20far%20been%20sold%20as%20a%20transparency%20law%20has%20been%20questioned%20as%20a%20probable%20conduit%20for%20quid%20pro%20quo-%20bribery%20between%20the%20anonymous%20donor%20and%20the%20state%2C%20and%20a%20possible%20money%20laundering%20mechanism%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20the%20declaration%20of%20who%20is%20paying%20which%20political%20outfit%20has%20been%20pronounced%20as%20indubitably%20essential%20to%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20exercise%20of%20choice%2C%20and%20thereby%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbasic%20structure%E2%80%9D%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20Government's%20Tryst%20with%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Should%20Neither%20Be%20Forgotten%20Nor%20Forgiven%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felectoral-bonds-narendra-modi-rbi%5C%22%3EModi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Tryst%20with%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Should%20Neither%20Be%20Forgotten%20Nor%20Forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBonds%20already%20bought%20but%20not%20deposited%20are%20%E2%80%98directed%E2%80%99%20to%20be%20returned%2C%20although%20the%20further%20question%20of%20what%20is%20to%20happen%20to%20moneys%20already%20collected%20by%20parties%20through%20means%20now%20held%20to%20be%20unconstitutional%20remains%20unaddressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20colossal%20advantage%20piled%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20through%20such%20collections%20is%20to%20be%20cancelled%2C%20then%20the%20kitty%20they%20have%20in%20possession%20from%20such%20unconstitutional%20collections%20must%20logically%20be%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInevitably%2C%20the%20other%20related%20question%20will%20also%20come%20to%20be%20asked%3A%20if%20forms%20of%20corruption%20in%20terms%20of%20quid%20pro%20quo%20and%20the%20investments%20from%20illicit%20sources%20come%20to%20be%20revealed%2C%20where%20may%20the%20buck%20of%20accountability%20stop%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20in%20particular%20must%20be%20of%20great%20relevance%20to%20a%20government%20that%20has%20routinely%20made%20loud%20noises%20about%20corruption%2C%20and%20thinks%20nothing%20of%20dispatching%20the%20ED%20here%2C%20there%20and%20elsewhere%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20or%20in%20pursuit%20of%C2%A0%20a%20vote%20or%20a%20whole%C2%A0%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%206%2C000%20or%20more%20crores%20garnered%20by%20the%20BJP%20may%20well%20have%20come%20in%20handy%20for%20conducting%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9COperation%20Lotus%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20for%20proliferating%20party%20assets%20in%20mind-boggling%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Caesar%E2%80%99s%20wife%20may%20come%20into%20consideration%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20shares%20the%20facts%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20side%20has%20argued%20in%20court%20that%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20the%20donor%20was%20put%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20such%20donors%20from%20likely%20vendetta%20after%20governmental%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20only%20another%20way%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20donations%20have%20been%20made%20to%20further%20the%20prospects%20both%20of%20the%20donor%20and%20of%20the%20ruling%20political%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20a%20nicely%20legalised%20sort%20of%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%20time%20has%20come%20to%20find%20a%20route%20to%20funding%20elections%20which%20obviates%20both%20corruption%20and%20undue%20lopsided%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20for%20long%20argued%20for%20a%20system%20of%20state-funding%20in%20which%20sums%20are%20allocated%20in%20accordance%20with%20agreed%20principles%20of%20distribution%20based%20on%20voter%20strength%2C%20or%20the%20strength%20of%20elected%20membership%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Selective%20Transparency%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Was%20Designed%20to%20Benefit%20the%20BJP%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-the-electoral-bonds-case-shows-bjps-politics-of-corruption-is-not-about-corruption-at-all%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Selective%20Transparency%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Was%20Designed%20to%20Benefit%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternately%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20argued%20that%20corporates%20could%20do%20the%20funding%2C%20but%20deposit%20their%20donations%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20broad%20daylight%2C%20and%20the%20Commission%20could%20then%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20make%20over%20funding%20to%20parties%20again%20on%20logical%20principles%20of%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20blow%20to%20bolster%20democracy%20offers%20quite%20the%20moment%20for%20the%20political%20class%20and%20its%20institutions%20to%20put%20their%20heads%20together%20and%20come%20up%20with%20reforms%20that%20bear%20the%20transparent%20promise%20of%20rendering%C2%A0%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20processes%20beyond%20reproach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20undoubtedly%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%20much%20more%20than%20the%20other%20mischievous%20idea%20currently%20under%20propagation%2C%20namely%20that%20of%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%2C%20which%20is%20again%20wholly%20violative%20of%20the%20other%20%E2%80%9Cbasic%20structure%E2%80%9D%20of%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20reinstatement%20of%20an%20all-important%20constitutional%20principle%20in%20defiance%20of%20state%20policy%20may%20give%20heart%20to%20public-spirited%20initiatives%20to%20lobby%20further%20to%20enhance%20the%20so-sanguine%20lead%20furnished%20by%20the%20honourable%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20the%20republic%20seize%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708504213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fillicit-bonds-scrapped-peoples-right-to-know-inseparable-from-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Clearly%20time%20has%20come%20to%20find%20a%20route%20to%20funding%20elections%20which%20obviates%20both%20corruption%20and%20undue%20lopsided%20advantage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fillicit-bonds-scrapped-peoples-right-to-know-inseparable-from-free-and-fair-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20detains%20Los%20Angeles%20ballerina%20'on%20suspicion%20of%20treason'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708504080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-kseniya-karelina-baller