usiness%20in%20June%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Berkhedi%20village%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Saroj%20was%20one%20among%20nine%20daughters.%20Her%20parents%20were%20farmers%20and%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20education%20opportunities%20for%20them.%20She%20spent%20her%20childhood%20on%20the%20fields%20watching%20her%20mother%20make%20food%20and%20pickles%2C%20eventually%20picking%20up%20the%20skills%20from%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20learnt%20to%20cook%20everything%2C%20what%20really%20fascinated%20her%20were%20pickles.%20She%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20she%20made%20a%20raw%20mango%20pickle%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20a%2015-year-old.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20that%20this%20would%20help%20her%20live%20her%20entrepreneurship%20dream%20almost%2018%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20was%20the%20norm%20then%2C%20she%20was%20married%20at%2020%20and%20moved%20to%20Shadora.%20Soon%2C%20she%20was%20busy%20with%20responsibilities%20at%20home%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20two%20children.%20But%20her%20husband%2C%20Bablu%20Prajapati%2C%20always%20encouraged%20her%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20had%20seen%20before%20marriage%20was%20our%20village.%20My%20husband%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339969%2Fadil-qadri-attar-perfumes-shark-tank-india-entrepreneur-asthma-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20me%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20matters%20of%20local%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saroj%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20to%20contribute%20to%20her%20community%2C%20she%20grabbed%20it%2C%20and%C2%A0%20served%20as%20the%20village%20sarpanch%20for%20eight%20years.%20During%20her%20tenure%2C%20she%20met%20many%20women%20from%