h%20growing%20bougainvillaeas%2C%20orchids%20and%20roses.%20She%20adds%20that%20she%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20flowers%20in%20her%20garden%2C%20and%20she%20even%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262213%2Fteenage-student-farmer-seed-machine-innovation-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20shared%20its%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20other%20people.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20on%20to%20Facebook%20and%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20interested%20in%20buying%20different%20plants.%20I%20also%20found%20many%20growing%20water%20plants.%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20my%20hand%20at%20that%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Viji%20bought%20her%20first%20water%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20bred%20flowers%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20protect%20the%20plant%20from%20dormancy%2C%20and%20I%20was%20also%20unsure%20how%20to%20re-pot%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20So%20she%20turned%20to%20the%20internet%20and%20joined%20various%20social%20media%20groups%20of%20planters%20and%20gardeners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20the%20International%20Waterlily%20and%20Water%20Gardening%20Society%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20discovered%20my%20people.%20Members%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311245%2F10-social-media-travel-groups-in-india-to-plan-backpacking-solo-trip-treks-adventure-itinerary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20groups%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20different%20countries%20across%20the%20oceans%20have%20stayed%20in%20touch%20with%20me%20ever%20since.%20They%20would%20offer%20guidance%20through%20video%20calls%2C%20advising%20me%20on%20whether%20my%20actions%20were%20right%20or%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20early%20days%20when%20she%20started%20growing%20water%20flowers%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20