20life.%20The%20circle%20of%20love%20was%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20an%20%3Cem%3Eajji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%20in%20Bengaluru%20shares%20how%20she%20was%20the%20sole%20caretaker%20of%20her%20two%20grandkids.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20wash%20their%20clothes%20and%20uniforms%20by%20hand%20every%20day.%20Now%20the%20washing%20machine%20I%20received%20through%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341516%2Fchennai-startup-global-green-coir-anees-ahmed-turns-coconut-husk-into-cocopeat-grow-bags%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20it%20easy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20me.%20In%20the%20time%20that%20I%20would%20spend%20hand-washing%20the%20clothes%2C%20I%20now%20tell%20stories%20to%20my%20grandkids%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heartwarming%20tales%20highlight%20the%20core%20purpose%20that%20drives%20charitable%20donations%2C%20an%20intent%20to%20let%20someone%20experience%20the%20same%20joy%20you%20once%20did%20with%20an%20object%20of%20clothing%20or%20a%20toy.%20This%20is%20the%20foundational%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20created%20by%20Anushka%20Jain%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20computer%20science%20engineer%20who%20is%20now%20in%20her%20thirties%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98sharing%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20birthday%2C%20Anushka%20would%20ask%20her%20mother%20which%20NGO%20they%20would%20be%20visiting%20that%20year.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20one%20each%20time%2C%20you%20see.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mum%20would%20pick%20an%20NGO%20in%20the%20city%20and%20we%E2%80%99d%20take%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330673%2Fgi-tagged-mithai-sweets-of-india-dharwad-peda-bebinca-khaje-moa-mihidana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweets%20and%20snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ha