%2Fhyderabad-abhishek-agarwal-goodeebag-free-waste-recycling-service%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20question)%20and%20they%20will%20get%20a%20voucher%20in%20turn%20that%20they%20can%20use%20on%20their%20next%20purchase.%20So%20a%20customer%20is%20donating%20their%20old%20shoes%2C%20mattresses%2C%20suitcases%2C%20all%20while%20getting%20a%20discount%20on%20the%20new%20shoes%2C%20mattress%20and%20suitcase%20he%2Fshe%20purchases!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opacity%20in%20the%20donation%20gambit%20is%20thus%20erased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Share%20At%20Door%20Step%20is%20present%20in%2011%20countries%20and%20has%20recently%20also%20extended%20its%20services%20to%20Singapore%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341912%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShare%20At%20Door%20Step%20is%20present%20in%2011%20countries%20and%20has%20recently%20also%20extended%20its%20services%20to%20Singapore%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Anushka%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20individuals%20who%20wish%2